commit.message: README.md: Update date to 2020-07-10

Bump version to 1.1
Add package __version__ string, use that in setup.py
generate_schema.py: Revert to the old behavior when --ignore_invalid_lines is not given, throws an exception upon the very first error and stops (#49)

/github/workflows: Better formatting for readability
